NK039(ti)030:1: // ma cig rang byung rgyal mo'i mchod gsol 'bring po ngo mtshar 'dod 'jo'i rol mtsho bzhugs /
NK039(ti)030:2: dpal ldan khrag 'thung bdag med mkha' 'gro'i gar //
NK039(ti)030:3: bdud bzhi'i ro la rnam bsgyur bla ma dang //
NK039(ti)030:4: gnyis med srung ma mchog der gus btud nas //
NK039(ti)030:5: yum chen mchod pa'i cho ga rnam par dbye //
NK039(ti)030:13: sman rag phyi nang gi mchod pas g.yon du bskor ba'i mdun stegs dang /
NK039(ti)030:14: rang gi mdun na rdor dril /
NK039(ti)030:18: rkang gi gling bu sogs tshogs par byas la /
NK039(ti)030:19: bdag gi rnal 'byor bzlas pa bsdu ldang gi bya ba bcas mthar phyin par byas te /
NK039(ti)030:23: stong pa'i ngang las dur khrod rol pa'i gzhal med
NK039(ti)030:24: chen por b+h+r+aum +aahmh'u 'od du zhu ba las byung
NK039(ti)030:25: ba'i phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod rdzas /
NK039(ti)030:26: ngo bo stong nyid la rnam pa bde stong gi
NK039(ti)030:27: ye shes mchod pa'i sprin rab 'byams su 'char bar
NK039(ti)030:28: gyur / sarba bid+pu ra sogs dang /
NK039(ti)030:29: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya dang /
NK039(ti)030:30: badz+ra ar+g+ham nas shap+ta'i bar dang /
NK039(ti)030:31: ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)030:41: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par byed /
NK039(ti)030:42: de yi ched du dpal ldan lha mo nag mo bsgom par bya'o //
NK039(ti)030:44: stong pa'i ngang las mdun du yam 'od du zhu ba las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu /
NK039(ti)030:45: dbyibs gru bzhi rgya che la 'phang mtho ba nang stong par bsgom /
NK039(ti)030:46: de yi nang gi dbus su ram 'od du zhu
NK039(ti)030:47: ba las me yi dkyil 'khor dmar po dbyibs rlung
NK039(ti)030:49: de yi steng du b+h+r+aum 'od du zhu ba las
NK039(ti)030:50: chu srin bye ba sa ya'i thod pa'i rtsig rmang
NK039(ti)030:51: / dregs pa'i thod dgu'i rtsig pa /
NK039(ti)030:52: thod pa'i gzhal yas khang dbyibs gru bzhi 'phang mtho
NK039(ti)030:53: la rgya che ba bse smug po'i sgo bzhi rta
NK039(ti)030:54: babs 'dod snam g.yu 'od sngon po 'bar ba'i mda'
NK039(ti)030:55: yab kyi logs dang bcas pa /
NK039(ti)030:56: zhing chen tshal pa dang gson po gcal du bkram pa'i gdan /
NK039(ti)030:57: don snod dbang po'i rgyan gyis nye bar spras shing
NK039(ti)030:58: gru gsum zla gam khrag mtsho thod rwa gru chad
NK039(ti)030:59: khrag khyam dang bcas pa'i lha gnas su ro yi
NK039(ti)030:60: gdan bsgyel ba / rus pa'i sku mkhar lcogs chung
NK039(ti)030:61: gi glo 'bur 'og gnam lcags urmo'i gzer gyis btab
NK039(ti)030:62: pa'i dur khrod chen po'i sa gzhi /
NK039(ti)030:63: mi ro dang rta ro gcal du bkram pa /
NK039(ti)030:64: mi khrag dang rta khrag gi 'dam bsgyel ba /
NK039(ti)030:65: dgra bgegs kyi snying khrag zhag tu 'khrugs pa'i rgya mtsho /
NK039(ti)030:66: me rlung 'ur 'ur 'thab pa'i gnam lcags 'bar ba'i
NK039(ti)030:67: ri bo 'jigs su rung ba dang bcas par gsal
NK039(ti)030:68: bar gyur / thod khang de yi nang dbus su
NK039(ti)030:69: rang nyid yi dam gyi lte ba nas yi ge
NK039(ti)030:70: ti nag po gcig spros 'od du zhu ba las
NK039(ti)030:71: sprul pa'i bong bu dmar gwa dbo dkar ba /
NK039(ti)030:72: rna ba gnyis dkrog chung byed cing rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i dbus su rgyug pa /
NK039(ti)030:73: rlung gi gshog pa g.yengs shing /
NK039(ti)030:74: rdzu 'phrul myur mgyogs kyi rtsal can //
NK039(ti)030:75: zhing lpags kyi stan btod cing /
NK039(ti)030:76: sga yi snga ru srin po'i yan 'gal dang rin po che 'bar bas mtshan cing /
NK039(ti)030:77: srin mo'i man 'gal gnyer ma'i lpags pa skam rid khrol ma las phyi ru byas pa /
NK039(ti)030:78: lpags pa'i sga g.yog dang sbrul nag gi gong thag dang glo nan /
NK039(ti)030:79: zhing chung ngu gnyis kyi smed byil skra mdud smed
NK039(ti)030:80: thung la yar btags pa'i lag pa gnyis 'phyang ba
NK039(ti)030:82: byi ru dang rgyu ma'i thur srab mi mgo skam
NK039(ti)030:83: po stong pa'i dom dom g.yer kha'i d+r+wa bas rgyan
NK039(ti)030:84: pa / rus sbal nag po'i phog gu btab cing /
NK039(ti)030:85: snga shad la khram bam dang /
NK039(ti)030:87: phyi shad la byang dmar bam po dang /
NK039(ti)030:88: nad kyi rkyal pa bkal pa /
NK039(ti)030:89: mjug ma'i g.yas g.yon ye shes kyi mig gnyis lhag
NK039(ti)030:90: por blta ba'i sga gong du ram las nyi ma'i
NK039(ti)030:92: de nas rang nyid yi dam gyi thugs ka nas yi ge mahnaga po gcig spros /
NK039(ti)030:93: bong bu'i sga gong nyi ma'i thog tu bab /
NK039(ti)030:94: mah'oda du zhu ba las ral gri yu ba mar bstan pa /
NK039(ti)030:96: gzhung pa rang la bstan pa /
NK039(ti)030:97: so yu'i mtshams su nyi ma'i thog tu mahnaga mos mtshan par bsgom /
NK039(ti)030:98: de nas ral gri las 'od zer 'phros /
NK039(ti)030:99: 'jig rten gyi mkha' 'gro ma thams cad la phog /
NK039(ti)030:100: thams cad lha mo nag mo nyid du gyur /
NK039(ti)030:101: kun tshur 'dus ral gri la thim //
NK039(ti)030:103: ru ru ro tsa pa la a shug+me h'u b+h+yo
NK039(ti)030:104: dza dzah dpal ye shes kyi lha mo nag mo'i
NK039(ti)030:105: skur gyur te / sku mdog nag mo nag po'i sprin dang bung ba ltar gnag pa /
NK039(ti)030:106: shin tu sgeg cing gtum rngam bzod par dka' ba'i gzi byin can zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK039(ti)030:107: spyan gsum dmar po khams gsum du bzlog cing gzigs pa /
NK039(ti)030:108: mi ro reng po zhal du bcug nas rno gdug gi mche ba bzhi gtsig pa /
NK039(ti)030:109: phyag g.yas sdig pa can gyi khro chu'i ral gri snyan g.yas kyi thad nam mkha'i la 'phyar ba /
NK039(ti)030:110: g.yon pas bdud khrag gis bkang ba'i thod pa zhal du stob pa'i tshul gyis thugs kar bsnams shing /
NK039(ti)030:111: mchan gyi s+t+wa zur g.yon na ne'u le'i rkyal pa rin po ches bkang ba 'dzin pa /
NK039(ti)030:112: bong bu la phyir log tu bcib cing /
NK039(ti)030:113: mi yi thod pa'i yob chen la bardzisa pa /
NK039(ti)030:114: dbu skra khams nag gyen du thor tshugs su mtho ba klu rje'u rigs kyis bcings shing /
NK039(ti)030:115: thur du yang sa la bshal ba'i gseb nas me stag 'phro ba /
NK039(ti)030:116: ral pa'i skra mtshams nas tshur thod pa skam po bcu drug gi phreng ba'i rtsa chings dang /
NK039(ti)030:117: rin po che'i rtse bran can gyi thod skam lngas dbu brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)030:118: spyi bor zla ba tshes brgyad pa dang /
NK039(ti)030:119: rma bya'i mdongs kyis brgyan cing /
NK039(ti)030:120: snyan cha g.yas na gser gyi 'khor lo rtsib brgyad
NK039(ti)030:121: pa'i thog tu dung gi seng ge dkar mo g.yu
NK039(ti)030:122: yi ral pa can 'phyo zhing g.yon na sbrul nag
NK039(ti)030:123: gi mgul pa las gser gyi dril bu bsil pa
NK039(ti)030:124: / lha ma yin he ran ke shu la sogs
NK039(ti)030:125: pa'i thod pa'i do shal se ral khar thogs pa
NK039(ti)030:126: / dang / sku stod la zhing lpags kyi na bza' gsol ba /
NK039(ti)030:127: sku smad kyi rnam bu g.yas phyogs su smug ma'i re lde dang /
NK039(ti)030:128: g.yon pas glang po che'i ko rlon las byas pa /
NK039(ti)030:129: stag lpags kyi sham thabs la sbrul nag gi sku rags bcings pa /
NK039(ti)030:131: rus pa'i rgyan cha lngas mdzes pa /
NK039(ti)030:132: klu chen brgyad gshib pa'i ska rags /
NK039(ti)030:133: sku la khrag gi thig le /
NK039(ti)030:135: thal chen gyi tshom bu btab pa /
NK039(ti)030:136: zhabs la dbang gi lcags sgrog bcings shing ye shes kyi me rlung 'tshubs ma'i dbus na 'gying ba'o //
NK039(ti)030:137: bong bu'i kha ngur zhabs su skems ma chu srin
NK039(ti)030:138: gyi mgo can sku mdog dmar nag zhal gcig phyag
NK039(ti)030:139: gnyis / g.yas kyis bong bu kha khrid cing g.yon na sbrul zhag gi zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)030:140: zhing lpags kyi sham thabs can /
NK039(ti)030:141: sbrul nag gi se ral khar thogs pa /
NK039(ti)030:142: gru gsum zla gam ngos na /
NK039(ti)030:143: gtso mo'i mdun na gsum re /
NK039(ti)030:144: g.yas g.yon na gnyis re bcas pa'i ma bdun ni /
NK039(ti)030:145: kun grags kun bzang kun gsal mo //
NK039(ti)030:146: ye shes mchog dang 'od chags ma //
NK039(ti)030:147: gsal 'phro rdo rje g.yu sgron bcas //
NK039(ti)030:148: nag mo gri thod gar gyis rol //
NK039(ti)030:149: zur gsum ma gsum dza dzi dzu //
NK039(ti)030:150: lcags kyu thod khrag ldag cing rngam //
NK039(ti)030:151: de yi phyi rol gru chad la //
NK039(ti)030:152: dkar sngo dmar ser sring mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)030:153: seng stag 'brug spyang gdong mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)030:154: ba dan thod khrag 'thung zhing gtum //
NK039(ti)030:155: khrag khyam shar lho nub byang na //
NK039(ti)030:156: zhi rgyas dbang drag las mdzad pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:157: bdun bdun dbang phyug nyer brgyad smug /
NK039(ti)030:158: rdo rje dung dmar thogs pa brjid //
NK039(ti)030:159: de thams cad kyang zhing gi gdan la me ri
NK039(ti)030:160: gos su gyon cing rlung 'tshubs chibs su bcib pa
NK039(ti)030:161: / ral pa nag po thur du gtib cing /
NK039(ti)030:163: bstan dgra dam nyams pa gang na 'dug kyang yam dang smyo 'bog nad sprin char du 'bebs shing /
NK039(ti)030:164: mche rtse dgra s+t+wa ltar gzas pa /
NK039(ti)030:165: dur khrod chas kyis brgyan cing /
NK039(ti)030:166: sgrub pa po'i re ba yongs su skong bar byed pa'i bdag nyid can no //
NK039(ti)030:167: de yi phyi rol du b+h+yohyiga las skyes pa'i 'khor ma mo stong dang /
NK039(ti)030:168: bdud mo bye ba 'bum sde'i tshogs rnams te /
NK039(ti)030:175: bar snang la gnas pa rnams dang /
NK039(ti)030:176: dmod pa'i mtshon cha can dang /
NK039(ti)030:178: dur khrod kyi ma mo mkha' 'gro /
NK039(ti)030:179: sprul pa yang sprul bye ba 'bum sde dang bcas pa /
NK039(ti)030:180: gzugs dang lag cha sogs gcig tu ma nges pa /
NK039(ti)030:181: kun kyang phrin las rnam bzhi'i rol pa 'dod dgur bsgyur bas /
NK039(ti)030:182: sa dang nam mkha' bar snang gi khyon yongs su
NK039(ti)030:183: gang ba'i sprin chen po 'phro ba gcig tu gyur
NK039(ti)030:184: / lha mo'i spyi bor zla ba'i steng du dkar po /
NK039(ti)030:185: mgrin par pad+ma'i steng du +aahdamara po /
NK039(ti)030:186: thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du h'u mthing nag /
NK039(ti)030:187: 'khor gyi ma mo rnams kyi thugs kar b+h+yohmathinga nag res mtshan par gyur /
NK039(ti)030:189: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas ri
NK039(ti)030:190: rab kyi byang shar mtshams dpag bsam shing gi drung
NK039(ti)030:191: / mu le mthing gi mtsho nas /
NK039(ti)030:192: dpal lha mo nag mo ye shes pa 'dir bskyed
NK039(ti)030:193: pa dang 'dra ba gtso 'khor gzal yas khang dang
NK039(ti)030:194: bcas pa skad cig gis sprin gyis phung po gtib
NK039(ti)030:195: pa ltar byon nas dam tshig pa la thim par
NK039(ti)030:196: gyur / rdo rje ga go na'i rgya bcas /
NK039(ti)030:197: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa li badz+ra sa ma ya dzahdzah rnga rol dbyangs snyan gyis 'gyur ba sbyar te /
NK039(ti)030:199: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:200: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK039(ti)030:201: ma cig lha mo spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)030:202: byang shar mtshams nas gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:203: rkang pas dman pa'i sho lo ka gsum ma mo byang chub sems rgyud las te /
NK039(ti)030:204: 'jig byed chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:205: spyod pa rlabs chen gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:206: shugs drag mthu chen gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:207: khyab 'gro rtsal chen gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:208: dgra bgegs 'dul byed gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:209: yon tan 'chi bzlog gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:210: khrag 'thung chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:212: bdud kyi yum gcig gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:213: gshin rje'i lcam gcig gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:214: 'dod khams dbang phyug gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:215: mah 'tshubs ma stong du 'khyil ba'i dbus na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)030:216: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba dang //
NK039(ti)030:217: rlung dmar lta bu'i 'tshubs ma ni //
NK039(ti)030:218: sku yi gnas te rgyan gyi mchog /
NK039(ti)030:219: drag shul khyab 'gro glog gi bang //
NK039(ti)030:220: bsam pa tsam gyis gnas su byon //
NK039(ti)030:221: ma de yi tshul du gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:222: b+h+yoh lha yi nang nas u ma'i sras //
NK039(ti)030:223: bcom ldan 'od srung bstan pa la //
NK039(ti)030:224: sh+aakya seng ge mgon de yi //
NK039(ti)030:225: bstan pa srung bar smon lam btab //
NK039(ti)030:226: de nyid dus su smin pa yi //
NK039(ti)030:227: dpal ldan lha mo mthu chen gtso //
NK039(ti)030:228: chos skyong rgyal mo gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:229: b+h+yoh dpal ldan ma chen dbyings na rtag bzhugs kyang //
NK039(ti)030:230: sku gsung thugs kyi rnam 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK039(ti)030:231: sna tshogs 'jigs pa'i gzugs su bstan mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)030:232: srid gsum dbang mo 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:233: skye 'gags gnas gsum bral las ma g.yos kyang //
NK039(ti)030:234: sku mchog ri rab che dang 'khril mdzad cing //
NK039(ti)030:235: nyi zla lte ba'i thad nas sprul mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)030:236: srid gsum b+ha gar bsdud mdzad gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:237: dpal ldan lha mo 'gro kun byams pa mo //
NK039(ti)030:238: sems can kun la byams pa ma dang 'dra //
NK039(ti)030:239: mi bslu dam tshig rjes su dgongs mdzod la //
NK039(ti)030:240: bdag la brtser dgongs gnas 'di nyid du byon //
NK039(ti)030:241: b+h+yoh sngon tshe byang chub shing drung du //
NK039(ti)030:242: thub pa chen po'i spyan snga ru //
NK039(ti)030:243: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas ltar //
NK039(ti)030:244: sangs rgyas bstan pa srung ba dang //
NK039(ti)030:246: dpal ldan lha mo gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:247: ma ru rtse yi sgo 'gram du //
NK039(ti)030:248: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:249: khas blangs dam nas blos bskul gyis //
NK039(ti)030:250: dam tshig bzhin las gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:251: gsang sngags srung ma dam tshig can //
NK039(ti)030:252: 'khor bcas gshegs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:254: ru ru ro tsa pa la a shug+me h'u b+h+yo
NK039(ti)030:255: dzahdzah dzahmh'u bam hoh a gats+tsha ya a gats+tsha ya
NK039(ti)030:256: h'u dza / bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK039(ti)030:257: b+h+yoh rlung sprin shugs 'chang mgrin bzang dmar gwa'i gdan //
NK039(ti)030:258: dur khrod ro dbus mkha' 'gro mas bskor te /
NK039(ti)030:259: rgyu ba'i lha mo gtum rngams nga ro can //
NK039(ti)030:260: dpal ldan mthu chen 'khor bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:261: pad+ma ka ma la ye stam gsum pa ni /
NK039(ti)030:263: dbang gi lha phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad badz+ra sa ma dzahs spyan drangs /
NK039(ti)030:264: 'di la mngon par dbang bskur du gsol //
NK039(ti)030:265: zhes gsol ba btab pas thugs ka nas rigs kyi yum bzhi bum pa thogs pa spros /
NK039(ti)030:266: sarba ta tha ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h'u /
NK039(ti)030:267: zhes gsungs shing khrus byas pas /
NK039(ti)030:268: dri ma thams cad chu yi rgyun gyis sku lus dkar lhag ger gyur /
NK039(ti)030:269: dbang rtags su ral pa'i rtsa ba thod pa bcu drug gi mdun nas brtsams /
NK039(ti)030:270: ko'u ri ma la sogs te gnas yul gyi ma mo bcu drug gis dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK039(ti)030:271: spyi bor pad zla nyi ma'i gdan la bla ma
NK039(ti)030:272: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i
NK039(ti)030:273: sbyor mtshams nas byang sems ye shes kyi bdud rtsis
NK039(ti)030:274: ma mo'i lus thams cad gang /
NK039(ti)030:276: mthu stobs nus pa'i gzi byin mchog tu 'bar /
NK039(ti)030:277: rang gi dam tshig nyams chag thams cad dag /
NK039(ti)030:279: rdo rje sems dpa' ma mo la thim pas /
NK039(ti)030:280: mthu stobs nus pa mchog tu 'bar bar gyur /
NK039(ti)030:281: yi ge brgya pa lan bdun bzla /
NK039(ti)030:282: 'di ni dam tshig bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK039(ti)030:283: bsre ba'i mchog ste srog gi snying //
NK039(ti)030:284: dam tshig rnams las 'da' ma byed //
NK039(ti)030:285: snying dang snying gi bur bya'o //
NK039(ti)030:286: ma h+aa pany+tsa sa ma ya a mri ta h'u /
NK039(ti)030:288: b+h+yoh gdod ma'i mgon po sh+aaka thub gsang ba'i bdag /
NK039(ti)030:289: d+ha na sang kri slob dpon pad+ma sogs //
NK039(ti)030:290: rab 'byams rtsa brgyud bla ma'i dam mnos bzhin //
NK039(ti)030:291: rnal 'byor bdag la ma sring bu ltar skyobs //
NK039(ti)030:292: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa li de wi badz+ra sa ma ya rak+shan+tu /
NK039(ti)030:294: b+h+yoh bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni //
NK039(ti)030:295: kha dog yi ge mtshan ma'i dpe bral yang //
NK039(ti)030:296: bsam gyis mi khyab nyams brgyar shar ba'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)030:297: mthu chen drag shul dpal ldan ma mo ni //
NK039(ti)030:298: rtsa brgyud bla ma'i ngo bor mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:299: yi dam dkyil 'khor mchog tu mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:300: ma mo mthu chen mkha' 'gror mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:301: bstan srung kun gyi gtso bor mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:302: skal ldan skyongs ma chen mor mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:303: rig 'dzin srung ma mchog tu mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:304: mna' zan rnams kyi gshed por mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:305: dus gsum nad kyi sman par mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:306: dam nyams zhing bcu'i gshed du mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:307: sa lam bar chad sel mdzad mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:308: nyams pa'i snying khrag 'thung bar mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:309: chos 'khor skyongs ba'i srung mar mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:310: rnal 'byor bdag gi mgon du mngal gsol lo //
NK039(ti)030:311: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:321: b+h+yoh nag mo khrag 'thung rdo rje ral pa can //
NK039(ti)030:322: dbang chen rdo rje thog dang ser chen 'beb //
NK039(ti)030:323: khams gsum sgral mdzad srid gsum rtsad nas gcod //
NK039(ti)030:324: ral pa bsigs pas stong gsum kun tu khyab //
NK039(ti)030:325: mche ba gtsigs pas dgra bgegs zhal du 'dren //
NK039(ti)030:326: ma lus dbang du bsdud la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)030:327: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa li re ma ti na mo na ma mi pra tits+tsha ho /
NK039(ti)030:329: yan lag brgyad ldan bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'khyil //
NK039(ti)030:330: dri bzang sbyar ba 'chi med zhabs bsil chu //
NK039(ti)030:331: rnam bkra yid 'ong chu skyes 'dabs bzang bzhad //
NK039(ti)030:332: lhan skyes sbyar ba'i dri bzang zhing kun khyab //
NK039(ti)030:333: nor bu nyi zla gsal byed sgron ma rdal //
NK039(ti)030:334: ga bur tsan+dana gurguma byugs pa'i chab //
NK039(ti)030:335: ro brgya lha yi bza' ba stong du dkrigs //
NK039(ti)030:336: dung dang sil chol snyan pa'i rol mo yis /
NK039(ti)030:337: dpal ldan ma chen srid gsum dbang mo ni //
NK039(ti)030:338: kun tu mnyes pa'i mchod sprin chen po ru //
NK039(ti)030:339: thogs med ting 'dzin blo yis legs sprul te //
NK039(ti)030:340: sna tshogs srid pa khyab pa'i bkod pas mchod //
NK039(ti)030:341: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa li de wi sa p+aa ri
NK039(ti)030:342: wa ra badz+ra ar+g+ham nas shap+ta pra tits+tsha ye s+w+aa
NK039(ti)030:344: kyee ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:345: ma khyod la gzugs kyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:346: lha mo'i gzugs dang klu mo'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)030:347: bzang ba'i gzugs dang brjid pa'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)030:348: kha dog sna tshogs mdzes pa'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)030:349: cir yang bsgyur ba'i gzugs la sogs //
NK039(ti)030:350: ma cig spyan la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)030:351: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /

NK039(ti)030:353: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:354: ma khyod la mchod pa sna tshogs 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:355: me tog chu skyes thang skyes rnam pa mang po dang //
NK039(ti)030:356: bzang zhing 'bras bu phun sum tshogs /
NK039(ti)030:357: ma cig sku la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)030:358: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)030:359: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)030:360: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:361: ma khyod la sgra yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:362: pi wam gling bu 'khar ba'i rnga //
NK039(ti)030:363: rdza rnga cang te'u g+han+de dung //
NK039(ti)030:364: cha lang sil snyan la sogs te //
NK039(ti)030:365: dril bu rnga dbyangs sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)030:366: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK039(ti)030:367: ma cig snyan la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)030:368: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)030:369: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)030:370: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:371: ma khyed la dri yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:372: a ka ru dang du ru ka /
NK039(ti)030:373: sha ka ra dang lnga sbyar ba'i //
NK039(ti)030:374: tsan+dana dkar dmar dri spos chab //
NK039(ti)030:375: ma cig thugs kar thugs mchog dngos grub ma cig
NK039(ti)030:376: ma khyed la ro yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni
NK039(ti)030:377: // lha yi zas sna dam nyams kyi //
NK039(ti)030:378: snying gi khu bas legs sbyar ba //
NK039(ti)030:379: zhal zas sha khrag rus par bcas //
NK039(ti)030:380: ma yi ljags thugs mchog dngos grub ma cig ma khyed la reg bya'i mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:381: stag glang zhing gi shun pa dang //
NK039(ti)030:382: lha rdzas dar sna'i gos bzang po //
NK039(ti)030:383: ma cig sku la thugs mchog dngos grub sh+ri ma
NK039(ti)030:384: h+aa k+aa li de wi re ma ti r+au pa
NK039(ti)030:385: shap+ta gan+d+he ra sa spar+she a h'u /
NK039(ti)030:392: stong pa'i ngang las gtor ma'i steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo /
NK039(ti)030:393: bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'og dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag rus pa'i phung po /
NK039(ti)030:395: snying po sha lngas khyab pa /
NK039(ti)030:396: don ye shes lnga yi mchod pa bla na med par spro bar gyur /
NK039(ti)030:399: ma mo gtor stegs kyi steng du bzhugs nas ljags
NK039(ti)030:400: rdo rje'i sbu gus gtor ma'i bcud drang ste gsol
NK039(ti)030:402: ma pham dpal ldan lha mo ni //
NK039(ti)030:403: snying rje'i ro yis rtag dga' bas //
NK039(ti)030:404: 'khor ba'i khrag mtsho rgyas par rol //
NK039(ti)030:405: dngos grub zhal ni mche ba gtsigs //
NK039(ti)030:406: mgon med 'gro la mthus skyobs kyang //
NK039(ti)030:407: nyams pa gsod pas sdig can gyi //
NK039(ti)030:408: srog gi shan pa mi bzad kyang //
NK039(ti)030:409: byang chub sems ni ches 'phel ba //
NK039(ti)030:410: 'gal ba med pa ma lags sam //
NK039(ti)030:411: de lta'i ya mtshan lha mo de //
NK039(ti)030:412: rmad byung til mar mtsho dbus na //
NK039(ti)030:414: me za brag gyon rgya mtsho'i klong //
NK039(ti)030:415: skem skya mtshan mo nag mo ni //
NK039(ti)030:419: skal mtshungs tshul ston 'byung po ma //
NK039(ti)030:421: dur khrod brgyad na 'grim mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)030:422: cang te 'u ni drag tu dkrol //
NK039(ti)030:423: rus pa'i rgyas cha si li li //
NK039(ti)030:424: mi rkang gling bu kyu ru ru //
NK039(ti)030:425: ma mo mkha' 'gro sna tshogs bskor //
NK039(ti)030:426: mah tshogs kyi gtso mo gtor ma'i las //
NK039(ti)030:427: kun tu bsgrubs pa gnas yul nyul //
NK039(ti)030:428: rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyi yum //
NK039(ti)030:429: rigs sngags 'chang la bde chen spel //
NK039(ti)030:430: 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi yum mdzad tsa //
NK039(ti)030:431: dbyangs can lha mo zhes su grags //
NK039(ti)030:432: spyan ras gzigs yum mdzad tsa na //
NK039(ti)030:433: gsang ba ye shes mkha' 'gro'i gtso //
NK039(ti)030:434: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i yum gyur par //
NK039(ti)030:435: gtum mo zhes grags res 'gar yang //
NK039(ti)030:436: de dag kun gyi 'bangs gyur ma //
NK039(ti)030:437: yid 'ong ri dwags mig can sku //
NK039(ti)030:438: dkar mo dung skyong dbyar zla rar //
NK039(ti)030:439: mnga' mdzad zha tshul rin chen rgyan //
NK039(ti)030:442: rin chen lhun po sbags 'dra ba //
NK039(ti)030:443: tshe g.yang bdag mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:444: lha mo brgyad kyi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK039(ti)030:445: 'jig rten yid la dbang med pa //
NK039(ti)030:447: yid 'phrog pad rag lhun po bzhin //
NK039(ti)030:448: khams gsum dbang bsdud rig byed ma //
NK039(ti)030:449: ston dang dpyid zla ra ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:450: dbang bsgyur rgyal mo lha mo'i mtshan //
NK039(ti)030:451: drag shul ma rung srin mo yi //
NK039(ti)030:452: gzugs 'dzin khyod ni drag po ste //
NK039(ti)030:453: dgun gyi nam la dgra bo bcom //
NK039(ti)030:454: mtha' yas mthu dang rdzu 'phrul gter //
NK039(ti)030:455: sad dang ser ba'i sna 'dren ma //
NK039(ti)030:456: nad dang rim gyis bdag mo ste //
NK039(ti)030:458: 'chi med sman gyi lha mo'ang yin //
NK039(ti)030:459: cir yang 'phrul ba'i sems ma ni //
NK039(ti)030:460: mchod bstod gsol lo gtor mas mchod //
NK039(ti)030:461: gtor ma'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:463: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK039(ti)030:464: bum dang ril dang phyed tshal dang //
NK039(ti)030:465: ku ku rta glang na ra sogs //
NK039(ti)030:466: sha chen thang dmar brdal bas mchod //
NK039(ti)030:467: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:468: ma cig thugs dam zhal zas snod //
NK039(ti)030:469: p+aa las b+han+d+ha bcud yangs pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:471: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:472: rdzong dang dka' bzlog nag mo che //
NK039(ti)030:473: gsol lo rol cig dgyes par mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:474: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:475: ma cig thugs dam zhal zas ni //
NK039(ti)030:476: gsod pa'i sha dang myos pa'i chang //
NK039(ti)030:477: bsregs pa'i bsur dang rlon pa'i sha //
NK039(ti)030:478: btsos pa'i sha dang khu ba khrag /
NK039(ti)030:479: nang rol glo snying mkhal ma bcas //
NK039(ti)030:480: gsol lo rol cig dgyes par mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:481: ma cig ma khyed la yid bzhin mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:482: 'bras bu lnga yi tshom bu bdud rtsi dang //
NK039(ti)030:483: koo ro tsa na dang ni dri chen dang //
NK039(ti)030:484: ma h+aa m+aam sa rak+ta tsit+ta ba su ta //
NK039(ti)030:485: ma cig zhal du thugs dam dngos grub gsol lo rol cig dgongs shig sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)030:486: ma mo byang chub sems rgyud las byung ba /
NK039(ti)030:487: ma mo 'dir spyon dam can rnams spyon cig /
NK039(ti)030:488: 'byung po 'byung mo'i sha ni zan bas zhim //
NK039(ti)030:489: ma mo dam can 'dir spyon khrag la spyon //
NK039(ti)030:490: 'byung po 'byung mo'i khrag ni chang bas zhim //
NK039(ti)030:491: ma mo dam can 'dir spyon rus la spyon //
NK039(ti)030:492: 'byung po 'byung mo'i rus pa mar bas zhim //
NK039(ti)030:493: sha khrag rus pa'i dam rdzas 'di gsol la //
NK039(ti)030:494: bdag gi bcol pa'i las 'di mthar dbyung zhig /

NK039(ti)030:496: u shug+mo h'u b+h+yo dzahdzah bam ma bam ma ma
NK039(ti)030:498: dgra bgegs kyi ma h+aa m+aam sa la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)030:499: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)030:500: ma h+aa tsit+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)030:501: ma h+aa ki ni ti la kh+aa h+ai /
NK039(ti)030:502: ma h+aa koo ro tsa na 'byung po'i phung po
NK039(ti)030:503: dgra bgegs 'di yi dbang po rnam lnga la ra
NK039(ti)030:504: rgya ram pa la shig shig rtog dpyod cig /
NK039(ti)030:505: ma b+h+yo ru ru kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)030:507: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK039(ti)030:508: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK039(ti)030:509: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK039(ti)030:510: ye shes lnga yi grub pa'i rdzas //
NK039(ti)030:511: rgyud drug sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK039(ti)030:512: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK039(ti)030:513: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK039(ti)030:514: byang chub sems ma'i tshogs chen dang //
NK039(ti)030:515: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK039(ti)030:516: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen dang //
NK039(ti)030:517: lha dang lha min gsang ba'i bdag /
NK039(ti)030:518: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:519: 'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK039(ti)030:520: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK039(ti)030:521: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid las //
NK039(ti)030:522: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK039(ti)030:523: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK039(ti)030:524: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)030:525: na ma sarba t+aa th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+h+aam pra tits+tsha ho /
NK039(ti)030:526: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i bka' brgyud bla ma dang //
NK039(ti)030:527: dngos grub 'byung gnas rgyud sde'i dkyil 'khor lha //
NK039(ti)030:528: ye shes mkha' 'gro dam can rgya mtshor bcas //
NK039(ti)030:529: rnam par dag pa'i bdud rtsis mchod par bgyi //
NK039(ti)030:530: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ho /
NK039(ti)030:531: b+h+yoh rdo rje lha mo nag mo mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal //
NK039(ti)030:532: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun dang spyod yul gcig pa'i yum //
NK039(ti)030:533: khams gsum log par lta ba thams cad dbyings su sgrol //
NK039(ti)030:534: srid gsum log 'dren za bar byed pa'i yum rnams la //
NK039(ti)030:535: rnam par dag pa'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa 'bul //
NK039(ti)030:536: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub rgya mtsho stsol //
NK039(ti)030:537: na ma sarba ta tha ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa
NK039(ti)030:538: a mri ta ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha la kha ram kha
NK039(ti)030:539: hi / dbang phyug chen mo kun gyi sring //
NK039(ti)030:540: rnal 'byor kun gyi ma cig mo //
NK039(ti)030:541: mtshan bzang nag mo re m+aa ti //
NK039(ti)030:542: ma stong ma mo'i 'khor tshogs la //
NK039(ti)030:543: rnam dag dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bul //
NK039(ti)030:544: thugs rjes brtse bas bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:545: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)030:547: chags pa khams gsum snying gi rak+ta ni //
NK039(ti)030:548: dmar ser lbu phreng chal chil g.yo ba can //
NK039(ti)030:549: rnam par 'khrugs pa'i zhag gi rgya mtsho las //
NK039(ti)030:550: rba rlab dam rdzas khol ba bdag gir bzhes //
NK039(ti)030:551: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)030:553: b+h+yoh stong gsum khyon la 'phya bas brgal nus pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:554: rnam dag yid kyi do rar ting 'dzin gar //
NK039(ti)030:555: rab bsgyur shes rab stong pa'i smin legs ma'i //
NK039(ti)030:556: phyag na dzam+bu gser gyi yo go'i dbus //
NK039(ti)030:557: phyur bur srungs pa'i rnam mang mchod pa'i gter //
NK039(ti)030:558: dpag yas phun tshogs 'od stong 'phro ba'i mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:559: kun bzang rnam par rol pa las byung ba'i //
NK039(ti)030:560: bde chen rdo rje'i 'khor los bde bar rol //
NK039(ti)030:561: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga tasogs nam mkha' mdzod sngags rgya bya /
NK039(ti)030:563: e yig rol pa chos 'byung gtum mo'i mes //
NK039(ti)030:564: wam dkar khu bar bzhus nas blugs pa'i rgyun //
NK039(ti)030:565: sems kyi rdo rje bung bas 'thung ba las //
NK039(ti)030:566: legs byung bde stong sbrang rtsi'i mchod yon stobs //
NK039(ti)030:567: don dam lha lam yangs pa'i pad dkar snod //
NK039(ti)030:568: rnam rtog phye mar 'thags pa ro mnyam bcud //
NK039(ti)030:569: rdzogs pa chen pos sbyar ba las byung ba'i //
NK039(ti)030:570: gnyis med bshos bu gtor ma'i 'jig rten 'bul //
NK039(ti)030:571: khams gsum rgyu ba yon bor 'khyogs pa'i mig /
NK039(ti)030:572: blo bral zur mdangs bkug pa'i lhan skyes kyi //
NK039(ti)030:573: mdza' na d+h+au tir sbyor bas dga' ba yi //
NK039(ti)030:574: reg bya spros bral lus phra khyod kyi gnyen //
NK039(ti)030:575: ye shes rdo rje ral gri'i 'khrul 'khor gyis //
NK039(ti)030:576: bdag 'dzin bdud sde'i mgo bo phye ma brgyar //
NK039(ti)030:577: bkas pa las byung sgrol ba bde chen du //
NK039(ti)030:578: shar bas phyogs las rnam rgyal mtshon te mchod //
NK039(ti)030:581: b+h+yoh mi mngon dbyings nas bzhengs pa'i lha mo ni //
NK039(ti)030:582: dbang phyug sras mo dpal ldan dung skyong ma //
NK039(ti)030:583: srid gsum bdag mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)030:584: dpon g.yogs 'khor bcas bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:585: thog med dus nas dug gsum dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)030:586: lus ngag yid gsum sdig bgyis bgyid du rtsal //
NK039(ti)030:587: bgyid la yi rangs mi dge sna tshogs bgyis //
NK039(ti)030:588: lha mo 'khor bcas khyed la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)030:589: sku yi dam tshig yi dam lha dang 'gal //
NK039(ti)030:590: gsung gi dam tshig sngags kyi bzlas brjod g.yol //
NK039(ti)030:591: thugs kyi dam tshig gsang ba spel ba 'di //
NK039(ti)030:592: lha mo 'khor dang bcas la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)030:593: sprul pa nal phrug bong dril ne'u le //
NK039(ti)030:594: gus pas mchod bstod ma byas khros shing brtsub //
NK039(ti)030:595: 'tshub ma spangs shing rten rdzas spangs ba rnams //
NK039(ti)030:596: lha mo 'khor dang bcas la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)030:597: nya stong la sogs dus kyis phyed pa la //
NK039(ti)030:598: bsnyen bsgrub bskang ba dus kyi cho ga chags //
NK039(ti)030:599: shes bzhin khyad du gsod pa ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)030:600: dam can srungs ma'i tshogs la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)030:601: bsrung bya ma srungs spang bya ma spangs dang //
NK039(ti)030:602: brten bya ma brten bsgrub bya ma bsgrubs pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:603: khas blangs dam bca' nyams pa ji mchis pa //
NK039(ti)030:604: bzod par gsol lo tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)030:605: bdag gi dus rnams kun tu lha khyod dang //
NK039(ti)030:606: skad cig mi 'bral phrin las rnam bzhi yis //
NK039(ti)030:607: nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam sems can ma lus rnams //
NK039(ti)030:608: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la 'god par shog /
NK039(ti)030:610: b+h+yoh rdo rje 'chang yum bde ba chen mo ni //
NK039(ti)030:611: char sprin dang mtshungs 'jig pa'i sku mdog can //
NK039(ti)030:612: drag shul ga zhas gdug pa'i snying 'byin pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:613: rno dkar che ba gangs ri lta bur gzengs //
NK039(ti)030:614: gdug pa dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar ba yi //
NK039(ti)030:615: smin ma 'khyogs pos bdud rigs gzhob tu bsreg /
NK039(ti)030:616: log 'dren snying chu tshom gyi rgyun las 'bab //
NK039(ti)030:617: a la ha la'i gad rgyang sa gsum g.yo //
NK039(ti)030:618: stong khams kun khyab phrin las rol pa 'dzin //
NK039(ti)030:619: cir yang 'char ba ma ma ru lu'i sgras //
NK039(ti)030:620: gsang ba mkha' 'gro ma tshogs dbang du bsdud //
NK039(ti)030:621: dur khrod chen po brgyad la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)030:622: phyag g.yas sra brtan rdo rje'i khrab chen kyang //
NK039(ti)030:623: brtan pa 'phrog ste dum bur 'dral ba yi //
NK039(ti)030:624: mthon mthing nam mkha'i mdangs 'tsher ral gri ni //
NK039(ti)030:625: rno ngar ldan pas dam log mgo bo gcod //
NK039(ti)030:626: lha min khrag gis bkang ba'i mi thod ni //
NK039(ti)030:627: dbang phyug myos pas dka' thub brtson pa bzhin //
NK039(ti)030:628: srin zhal nyer rlab chu gter 'khrugs pa ltar //
NK039(ti)030:629: rnam par sdud pa'i dbyings su legs par stobs //
NK039(ti)030:630: dpal ldan rmad byung 'gro ba'i ma ma ni //
NK039(ti)030:631: sku gsum rgyal ba'i bstan pa kun srung zhing //
NK039(ti)030:632: dam tshig ldan pa kun gyis mgon gyur pa //
NK039(ti)030:633: dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)030:634: b+h+yoh dbyings phyug dpal ldan rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
NK039(ti)030:635: 'gro ba thugs rjes skyongs phyir yum gyis tshul //
NK039(ti)030:636: mtshan ma'i skyon spangs sku mdog nag mor ston //
NK039(ti)030:637: drag shul spyod phyir gcer bu srin mo'i tshul //
NK039(ti)030:638: lha chen 'dul phyir sdang mig ral pa bsigs //
NK039(ti)030:639: skye shi rtsad gcod za byed mche ba gtsigs //
NK039(ti)030:640: 'khor ba ljags la 'dril phyir rkan sgra rdeb //
NK039(ti)030:641: dug lnga sel phyir rma bya'i mdangs kyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:642: byang chub sems ldan spyi gtsug zla rgyas gsal //
NK039(ti)030:643: dam tshig bya ra mdzad phyir spyan rtsa dmar //
NK039(ti)030:644: lha min g.yul ngo bzlog phyir mdung dang ru mtshon bsnams //
NK039(ti)030:645: srid gsum bsgral phyir shes rab ral gri bsnams //
NK039(ti)030:646: dgra bgegs 'dul phyir nad kyi rkyal pa thogs //
NK039(ti)030:647: dbul ba sel phyir ne'u le'i rkyal bu bsnams //
NK039(ti)030:648: 'chi bdag bzlog phyir snyan g.yas seng ges brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:649: gdug pa 'dul phyir klu dbang snyan chas brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:650: 'byung po 'dul phyir thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:651: rnal 'byor skyobs phyir dril chung sgra snyan sgrogs //
NK039(ti)030:652: klu chen 'dul phyir sbrul gyi ska rags bcings //
NK039(ti)030:653: bdud dpung dpa' bskum zhing lpags gos su gyon //
NK039(ti)030:654: theg chen don ldan glang chen ko rlon gsol //
NK039(ti)030:655: dpa' gtum bstan phyir stag gi sham thabs can //
NK039(ti)030:656: smon lam mi dor sku smad re ldes dkris //
NK039(ti)030:657: mdzes par bya phyir rkang sgrogs lcags las byas //
NK039(ti)030:658: nyon mongs mtsho skem lte bar nyi mas brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:659: srin po 'dul phyir chibs su bong bu bcib //
NK039(ti)030:660: stong gsum bgrod phyir 'tshubs ma'i klong na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)030:661: dur khrod gnas 'dir 'khor g.yog mang pos bskor //
NK039(ti)030:662: 'khor ba 'jigs tshe sdug bsngal sems can rnams //
NK039(ti)030:663: lha mo khyed kyi zhal du thams cad zhugs gyur te //
NK039(ti)030:664: brtse ldan thugs rjes 'gro kun skyobs mdzod cing //
NK039(ti)030:665: byang chub spyod pa'i thar lam gsal mdzad pa //
NK039(ti)030:666: lha mo mthu chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)030:667: b+h+yoh 'chi med lam kun gang ba'i chu 'dzin ni //
NK039(ti)030:668: dpag yas phyogs 'khor kun khyab dri bzhon bcas //
NK039(ti)030:669: mngon par mdzes pa'i dbus su rgyu ba la //
NK039(ti)030:670: chu srin mgo bos brgyan pa'i phra men mas //
NK039(ti)030:671: ba su ta yi zhags pas dam bzhag pa //
NK039(ti)030:672: rlung gi shugs 'chang mgrin bzang gwa pa'i steng //
NK039(ti)030:673: bsil zer bdud rtsir nyil ba'i ga bur dbang //
NK039(ti)030:674: rta bdun mo yi dbal 'chang 'od brgya pa //
NK039(ti)030:675: sku yi gnas nas mun pa'i mdangs 'phrog cing //
NK039(ti)030:676: ya mtshan pad dkar bzhad pa'i dpal 'dzin lha //
NK039(ti)030:677: lha mo khyed la dwangs ba'i sems kyis su //
NK039(ti)030:678: ji srid dran pa de srid mdun gyi mkha' //
NK039(ti)030:679: rab 'bar me rlung lding gur dbus na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)030:680: sna lnga'i 'ja' gur 'od kyi zil pa can //
NK039(ti)030:681: phun tshogs rkang 'thung 'khyil ba'i ljon bzang gi //
NK039(ti)030:682: 'dab ma las skyes khu bcud ro brgya pa //
NK039(ti)030:684: lha lam mun pas sbags 'dra khros pa'i skur //
NK039(ti)030:685: spyan zlum nor bu gsum 'khyil rno dkar tshem //
NK039(ti)030:686: gangs ri ltar mdzes glog dmar ljags su 'dril //
NK039(ti)030:687: lha min thod pa'i snod 'chang lha dmag rdzong //
NK039(ti)030:688: lto rlung chu khur 'khrigs pa'i dbus nas thon //
NK039(ti)030:689: thugs rjes li shi'i lding khang bsung zhim 'di //
NK039(ti)030:690: bstan pa 'dzin par mchod pa'i bdug sprin lags //
NK039(ti)030:691: gnam sngon dum bu blangs 'dra'i mtshon cha dang //
NK039(ti)030:692: rin chen gter snod 'dzin pa'i dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:693: 'khor ba khrag gi rgya mtshor rtag 'gro yang //
NK039(ti)030:694: zhi ba mya ngan 'das la phyir gzigs pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:695: 'dod 'byung dpag bsam yal ga dud pa ni //
NK039(ti)030:696: bde ba lhan skyes phang phung 'bras bu'i khur //
NK039(ti)030:697: rnam par rgyas 'dzin rnam dag lam bzang ros //
NK039(ti)030:698: skal pa sbom po'i skal ldan mtha' dag kun //
NK039(ti)030:699: rgyal ba'i bstan pa chu gter chen po ni //
NK039(ti)030:700: mang thos gru bo yongs 'dzin ded dpon gyis //
NK039(ti)030:701: drin las brgal te nges gsang rdo rje'i theg /
NK039(ti)030:702: rgyud don rin chen dbang rgyal nyer thob cing //
NK039(ti)030:703: bshad sgrub klung brgya 'du ba'i ma dros pa //
NK039(ti)030:704: bslab gsum gdengs ka rim gnyis 'od 'phro zhing //
NK039(ti)030:705: dge 'dun klu dbang tshogs kyis nyer bsten pa //
NK039(ti)030:706: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i dpal yon brgal bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:707: sh+aakya'i bstan pa'i bang mdzod 'gro 'di'i gnyen //
NK039(ti)030:708: rgud pa'i mi mthun srung ma khyed gnyer kha //
NK039(ti)030:709: sngon smon rten 'brel mthu yis rab bskos phyir //
NK039(ti)030:710: bsam pa'i re kun bsgrub mdzad ma la bstod /
NK039(ti)030:712: bsnyen pa 'bum bstod bskang gsol dang //
NK039(ti)030:713: bskul dang gtor ma 'degs mtha' bsdud //
NK039(ti)030:715: bdag yi dam du gsal ba'i thugs srog gi 'od
NK039(ti)030:716: kyis ma mo'i thugs kar phog thugs rgyud bskur bar
NK039(ti)030:717: gyur / gang non yi dam gyi rtsa sngags cung zad bzlas /
NK039(ti)030:718: ma mo'i thugs kar ha las lha mo koo'u ri
NK039(ti)030:719: ma sngon mo g.yas zhing dbyug g.yon thod khrag bsnams
NK039(ti)030:720: pa / de'i thugs kar zla ba'i steng du ral gri /
NK039(ti)030:721: de'i so yu'i mtshams na ma nag po gcig la
NK039(ti)030:722: yi ge bco lngas yongs su bskor ba bdag gi
NK039(ti)030:723: thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros sngags phreng la phog
NK039(ti)030:725: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK039(ti)030:726: sku gsung thugs kyi byin bsdus /
NK039(ti)030:728: bstan pa la sdang ba'i dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad /
NK039(ti)030:729: ye shes dang 'jig rten gyi ma mo snang srid
NK039(ti)030:730: dregs pa'i tshogs thams cad kyi srog gi snying po
NK039(ti)030:732: ma mo'i thugs srog la thim /
NK039(ti)030:733: gzi byin mchog tu 'bar ba'i 'od kyis phrin las rnam pa bzhi cir yang bsgrub bsam la /
NK039(ti)030:734: ru ru ro ru tsa pa la a shug+she h'u
NK039(ti)030:735: b+h+yohdza dzah zhes rdo rje nag mo dbang phyug ma'i
NK039(ti)030:736: rgyud kyi lugs kahthoga pas bzhed pa'i sngags bco lnga
NK039(ti)030:737: ma dang / yang 'phags ma lha mo nag mo'i rgyud las /
NK039(ti)030:738: ru ru ro ru tsa pa la a shug+she ma h'u ma b+h+yo dza dza /
NK039(ti)030:740: mahb+h+yohma ma b+h+yoh b+h+yo b+h+yo mah ma b+h+yohm /
NK039(ti)030:742: zhes b+h+yohbaduna ma dgu ma'i ma mo'i spyi dril bsnyen mthar /
NK039(ti)030:743: ma mo'i thugs ka nas 'od kyi phreng ba'i rang
NK039(ti)030:744: bzhin sngags kyi 'khor lo gnyis pa zhig byung nas
NK039(ti)030:745: rang gi thugs kar thim par bsam nas cung zad
NK039(ti)030:747: ni ye shes lnga ldan la //
NK039(ti)030:748: ru ru ko ri ro ru ni //
NK039(ti)030:749: seng ha tsa pa la ral gcig /
NK039(ti)030:750: a shug gsang ba'i ma bdun dang //
NK039(ti)030:751: ma h'u ma b+h+yo dza dzahni //
NK039(ti)030:756: sa p+aa ri wa ra i dam ba lin+ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)030:757: btags pa lan bdun nam gsum gyis 'bul /
NK039(ti)030:758: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa li de wi khrag 'thung gi rgyal mo /
NK039(ti)030:760: chos 'khor dang bas mtha' dang sde dgon gnyan po'i srung ma dam pa /
NK039(ti)030:761: ming brgya ma la mtshan stong ma /
NK039(ti)030:762: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bka' la sdod cing /
NK039(ti)030:764: rnal 'byor pa'i ma ma gcig pu /
NK039(ti)030:766: gtum rngams gsung gi ma mo /
NK039(ti)030:767: sprul pa thugs kyi ma mo /
NK039(ti)030:768: mi zad yon tan gyi ma mo /
NK039(ti)030:769: drag shul phrin las kyi ma mo /
NK039(ti)030:770: 'khor ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams
NK039(ti)030:771: kyis dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma rgyan gyis mchod
NK039(ti)030:777: skye bo sdang bar byed pa'i dgra thul /
NK039(ti)030:778: 'byung po gnod par byed pa'i bgegs choms /
NK039(ti)030:779: 'gal rkyen bar du gcod pa phyir bzlog /
NK039(ti)030:780: bsgral ba'i zhing rnams thal ba'i rdul du brlag ste /
NK039(ti)030:781: rgyud bskyed rdzogs rdzogs pa chen po'i bshad sgrub 'phel ba dang /
NK039(ti)030:782: lam rim pa gnyis gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir 'dus pa rnams la /
NK039(ti)030:783: mthun rkyen legs tshogs smon pa'i don thams cad myur
NK039(ti)030:784: ba nyid du 'grub pa'i phrin las rgya chen po
NK039(ti)030:786: b+h+yoh skye med rnam dag mkha' dbyings dag pa nas //
NK039(ti)030:787: snang la ma 'gags sna tshogs gzugs su shar //
NK039(ti)030:788: skye ba'i cho 'phrul 'bar ba'i skur ston pa //
NK039(ti)030:789: h'u las bskyed pa'i dpal chen he ru ka /
NK039(ti)030:790: ye shes thugs kyi khyad par chen po las //
NK039(ti)030:791: dur khrod dbyings nas phyag rgya'i skur gsal bar //
NK039(ti)030:792: mdog bzang nag mo ral pa'i zar bus brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:793: rgyan dang cha lugs sna tshogs 'jigs pas brjid //
NK039(ti)030:794: rlung 'tshub nang na sku yi phyag rgya gsal //
NK039(ti)030:795: rlung nag nang nas ral gri phyung ba'i tshul //
NK039(ti)030:796: dgra bo gang la bya ba rtsad gcod ma //
NK039(ti)030:797: g.yon na ne'u le'i rkyal pa thogs pa ni //
NK039(ti)030:798: log nyams mi mgo bcad pa sbed pa'i snod //
NK039(ti)030:799: sngon khyod dmod pa'i mtshon 'chang chen mo la //
NK039(ti)030:800: gsang ba pas zhus bla med he ru kas //
NK039(ti)030:801: sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor chen por legs btul nas //
NK039(ti)030:802: sbom po dbang mo nas bzung phyi nang gsang //
NK039(ti)030:803: dbang bskur sa brgyad non pa'i sems mar gyur //
NK039(ti)030:804: thig le chos kyi sku la mnyam gnas kyang //
NK039(ti)030:805: snang srid 'byung lnga b+ha ga yum lnga'i klong //
NK039(ti)030:806: sprul skus 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)030:807: sangs rgyas bstan la gnod pa za skal du //
NK039(ti)030:808: gtad nas rnam bzhi'i 'khor srungs bka' bsgos pa //
NK039(ti)030:809: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)030:810: phrin las rgya mtsho grub pa khyod la bstod //
NK039(ti)030:811: b+h+yoh yang dag don ldan ye shes lha mo ni //
NK039(ti)030:812: bskal mang sngon nas rgyal ba'i zhal mthong ba //
NK039(ti)030:813: ngang tshul cho rol gcig tu ma 'tshal yang //
NK039(ti)030:814: lha chen sras mo srin po'i chung mar gyur //
NK039(ti)030:815: lhag pa'i mthu can gshin rje'i bu mo la //
NK039(ti)030:816: ro thang nag por phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK039(ti)030:817: rta mgrin gsang dbang spyi bor rgyas btab cing //
NK039(ti)030:818: lus ngag yid la he ru ka dpal dang //
NK039(ti)030:819: thugs kyi dpal be'u rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas lnga //
NK039(ti)030:820: phra men bcu drug la sogs rgyan rnams dang //
NK039(ti)030:821: rdo rje pho nya drug cu rtsa bzhi ni //
NK039(ti)030:822: 'khor du dbang bskur mthu rtsal pha rol son //
NK039(ti)030:823: pad+ma dam pa'i dpal gyi sangs rgyas su //
NK039(ti)030:824: rgyal bas lung bstan da lta shes sgrib sbyong //
NK039(ti)030:825: srid gsum 'gran zla med la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)030:826: b+h+yoh lha chen sras mo ma pham ro langs ma //
NK039(ti)030:827: klu mo gzhog skam phur lha chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)030:828: khyod kyi khol mo re m+aa ti zhes grags //
NK039(ti)030:829: bstan srung bran du gyur la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)030:830: b+h+yoh nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)030:831: 'gro ba'i srog la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)030:832: ma gsum sring la sogs pa yis //
NK039(ti)030:833: bye ba phrag mang sprul la bstod //
NK039(ti)030:834: dbyar zhing nam mkha'i khams na rgyug /
NK039(ti)030:835: 'brug dang glog gi bdag po mdzad //
NK039(ti)030:836: lce dang bu yug 'beb mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)030:837: glog ma sprin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)030:838: dpyid cing kun la brod mdzod ma //
NK039(ti)030:839: chu bo kun gyi sna 'dren ma //
NK039(ti)030:840: chu bo kun gyi gzhung 'byams ma //
NK039(ti)030:841: nag mo gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)030:842: ston zhing 'bras bu smin mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)030:843: spang po de ni kha ser la //
NK039(ti)030:844: 'bru dang lo yi bcud len ma //
NK039(ti)030:845: mi rnams kun gyi dpal 'phrog ma //
NK039(ti)030:847: dgun zhing rgya mtsho'i gting na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)030:848: khams gsum kun gyis rgyas 'debs ma //
NK039(ti)030:849: klu 'brug kun gyis dgyes sde mo //
NK039(ti)030:855: stong pa'i ngang las gnas khang dur khrod drag po'i bkod pa 'byams klas pa'i dbus su //
NK039(ti)030:856: 'jigs rung thod pa bse lcags kyi mkhar //
NK039(ti)030:857: dam nyams pa'i dgra bo bsgral ba'i mgo rus don snod dbang lnga /
NK039(ti)030:860: srin gyi bong bu dmar gwa sogs /
NK039(ti)030:861: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod rdzas /
NK039(ti)030:865: khyad par gyi rdzas rnams ngo bo ye shes la /
NK039(ti)030:866: rnam pa lha rdzas kyi mchod sprin ma tshangs ba med pa /
NK039(ti)030:867: bde stong zag pa med pa'i dpal du cir yang 'char zhing rgyas par gyur cig /
NK039(ti)030:868: nam mdzod kyi sngags rgyas byin rlabs nas /
NK039(ti)030:869: b+h+yoh ma cig lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:870: sring gcig lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:871: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam gcig ma //
NK039(ti)030:872: nad dang rim gyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)030:873: thugs dam bskang phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:874: nyams chag sel phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:875: phrin las sgrub phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:877: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:878: 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:879: zhing chen g.yab mos thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:880: rang bzhin gnas nas spyan 'dren phyir //
NK039(ti)030:881: mi rkang gling bu'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:882: mchod pa'i mthun rdzas lags pas na //
NK039(ti)030:883: rol mo sgra yis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:884: dam tshig gnyan po bsre ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:885: bdud rtsi sman gyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:886: brten pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:887: mi dbang snying gis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:888: 'chi kha'i mtshal tig dmar po dang //
NK039(ti)030:889: rdo sol me yis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:890: dgos pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:891: shing lo rlung khyer sar ma lhung //
NK039(ti)030:892: dgyes pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:893: mchod yon zhabs bsil me tog dang //
NK039(ti)030:894: bdug spos mar me dri zhal zas //
NK039(ti)030:895: rol mo phyi yi mchod pa dang /
NK039(ti)030:896: gzugs sgra dri ro reg chos dang //
NK039(ti)030:897: mi rta glang khyi bya sha lnga //
NK039(ti)030:898: byang sems rgyud pa rak+ta sogs //
NK039(ti)030:899: bdud rtsi gsang mchod thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:900: mgrin pa'i gsang nas sbyor ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:901: ra bya dgra khrag thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:902: ljags kyi gza' ba'i dam rdzas slad //
NK039(ti)030:903: bshos gtsang chang khur sgog tsong dang //
NK039(ti)030:904: dgra bgegs sha khrag nal bu'i sha //
NK039(ti)030:905: sha rus tshogs kyis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:906: sgrub pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:907: rtag gtor chen pos thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:909: rgyun gtor chen pos thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:910: phyi nang gsang rten yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:911: bong bu gwa dmar lug nag dang //
NK039(ti)030:912: de mo rma bya dar nag po //
NK039(ti)030:913: b+han+dza rma bya nal bu yi //
NK039(ti)030:914: rgyal mtshan a mri ta myos byed //
NK039(ti)030:915: gri nal snying gis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:916: sku gsung thugs rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)030:917: bris lugs sku dang rnga dbyangs dang //
NK039(ti)030:918: dril bu cang te'u bskul ba'i sgra //
NK039(ti)030:919: dzaba dang ting 'dzin thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:920: 'dod khams gtso mo chen po la //
NK039(ti)030:921: rgyal srid bdun dang rdzas rtags brgyad //
NK039(ti)030:922: ri rab gling bzhi nyi zla dang //
NK039(ti)030:923: go khrab mtshon cha'i rigs thams cad //
NK039(ti)030:924: sku 'bag phod ka rus rgyan zhwa //
NK039(ti)030:925: phreng ba dar sna dpag bsam shing //
NK039(ti)030:926: thod pa lcags bse rin chen khang //
NK039(ti)030:927: lce spyang ri dwags g.yung dwags dang //
NK039(ti)030:928: chu gnas dbugs rkyal mda' dar sha /
NK039(ti)030:929: khrag nad bskyil ba'i dug rdzing mtsho //
NK039(ti)030:930: nad rkyal khram shing dpag bsam shing //
NK039(ti)030:931: tshon gyi gru gu sbrul zhags dang //
NK039(ti)030:933: me long sgra sbyar ting ting shag /
NK039(ti)030:934: sga dang lan tsha spod kyi rigs //
NK039(ti)030:935: tshil gsur rnam bya mi nag dang //
NK039(ti)030:937: 'jol ber nag po rna rgyan sbrul //
NK039(ti)030:938: seng ge dang ni gser 'khor dril //
NK039(ti)030:939: chu srin lpags dang zhing lpags dang //
NK039(ti)030:940: glang ko stag sham re lde dang //
NK039(ti)030:941: dung chen dmar bskyil ral gri dang //
NK039(ti)030:942: ne'u le rkyal la sogs pa //
NK039(ti)030:943: mthun rdzas kun gyis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:945: gzhan yang lha g.yag ngar sgras stong gsum kheng //
NK039(ti)030:946: gnam lcags rdo rje'i rwa rtses dgra bo'i snying //
NK039(ti)030:947: snying rjer 'dral ba gdug pa'i 'gying zhol can //
NK039(ti)030:948: lce dmar nam mkha'i khams su lhab lhab 'dis //
NK039(ti)030:949: re ti ma gsum ma bdun sring gdong bzhi //
NK039(ti)030:950: dbang phyug ma stong bye 'bum sprul pa'i 'khor //
NK039(ti)030:951: phyi rol dur khrod rgya mtsho la gnas pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:952: snang srid ma mo'i tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)030:953: thugs dam gnyan po 'di bskang nas //
NK039(ti)030:954: nyams chag gyur na bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)030:955: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)030:956: phrin las drag shul mthu ma chung //
NK039(ti)030:957: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:959: b+h+yoh kun tu bzang mo dbyings yum pha rol phyin //
NK039(ti)030:960: bde ba chen po'i dga' ma rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)030:961: gang 'dul sprul pa'i cho rol dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:962: skye med klong nas gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)030:963: snang ba 'khrul pa rtag 'khyams mkha' mnyam 'gro //
NK039(ti)030:964: srid mtshor thog ma med nas drin che ba //
NK039(ti)030:965: de kun gtan dang 'phral bde kun gyi sgo //
NK039(ti)030:966: thub bstan rin chen mchog las gzhan yod min //
NK039(ti)030:967: 'on kyang da dus snyigs ma'i mthar lhung bas //
NK039(ti)030:968: rgyal gsungs 'chad dang sgrub pa ches nyams shing //
NK039(ti)030:969: lhag par rdo rje'i theg dang bla med bstan //
NK039(ti)030:970: shin tu 'chal ba'i gling 'di'i bde skyid zad //
NK039(ti)030:971: khyad par gang la brten na tshe gcig gis //
NK039(ti)030:972: mig 'phrul lta bur 'ja' lus la bgrod thabs //
NK039(ti)030:973: dpal ldan mdo dang snying po'i rgyud kyi rgyal //
NK039(ti)030:974: 'dzin pa'i bstan 'dzin skyes bu ma dmigs sam //
NK039(ti)030:975: mchis kyang thos bsam slob sgrub phrin las tshogs //
NK039(ti)030:976: rim par 'gags las dngos grub gnyis kyi dpal //
NK039(ti)030:977: dgun gyi chu bzhin 'bri ba ma gzigs sam //
NK039(ti)030:978: rdo rje mkha' 'gro chen mo bran dang g.yog /
NK039(ti)030:979: sring gcig brtse ldan rdo rje'i dam tshig can //
NK039(ti)030:980: rgyal bstan spyi dang khyad par snying po'i bstan //
NK039(ti)030:981: sa yi steng 'dir rgyas pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:982: lhag par rtsa bar brgyud pa'i bla ma dang //
NK039(ti)030:983: rgyal ba gnyis pa kun mkhyen rdo rje 'chang //
NK039(ti)030:984: kahthoga pa yi spyan sngar khas blangs bzhin //
NK039(ti)030:985: bla med rgyud sde kun gyi spyi bo pa //
NK039(ti)030:986: gsang ba snying po'i bstan pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK039(ti)030:987: rig 'dzin dge slong dge 'dun 'dus pa'i sde //
NK039(ti)030:988: phyogs mthar dar zhing rgyas par mdzad du gsol //
NK039(ti)030:989: brtse ma mkha' 'gro khyod la mchod pa'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)030:990: rab 'byams nam mkha' gang bar yongs sprul te //
NK039(ti)030:991: gdug can bstan dgra bsgral ba'i sha khrag rus //
NK039(ti)030:992: rak+ta'i chu gter lbu ba'i phreng bar 'phar //
NK039(ti)030:993: dbang po rnam lnga'i bkrag mdangs 'od zer gsal //
NK039(ti)030:994: tshil chen bdug pa'i dud sprin mkha' la 'khyil //
NK039(ti)030:995: dmar gyi gtor ma brag ri khros pa 'dra //
NK039(ti)030:996: bdud rtsi a mri ta yis rba rlabs khol //
NK039(ti)030:997: zlos gar bsgyur ba'i bya nag klad la lding //
NK039(ti)030:998: mthun rdzas sna tshogs yid 'ong char ltar 'thib //
NK039(ti)030:999: ce spyang rnams mang ngur skad glu ru ldir //
NK039(ti)030:1000: rkyang shes gyi ling smug chung dre'u bong //
NK039(ti)030:1001: dmar gwa sbrul dang rus pa'i sga chas brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:1002: dngos su 'byor dang yid las rab byung ba //
NK039(ti)030:1003: phun tshogs srid pa'i dpal yon ci mchis kun //
NK039(ti)030:1004: lha mo khyed la dngas ba'i sems kyi 'bul //
NK039(ti)030:1005: nyams chag ma lus so sor bshags par bgyi //
NK039(ti)030:1006: bdag ni mi shes byis pa'i rang bzhin can //
NK039(ti)030:1007: khyed ni mkha' dbyings lta bu'i rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)030:1008: de phyir sku gsung thugs dang 'gal ba chags //
NK039(ti)030:1009: bsam pa 'grub pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)030:1012: 'di ma mo gsang rgyud las 'byung ba dngos su gab ste /
NK039(ti)030:1014: nad kyi bdag mo chen mo ste //
NK039(ti)030:1015: gshin rje'i lcam gyi sring gcig mo //
NK039(ti)030:1016: mdzes pa'i lan bu gcig ma la //
NK039(ti)030:1017: re lde mdzes pas rnam par brgyan //
NK039(ti)030:1018: cha lugs ma lus 'chang byed ma //
NK039(ti)030:1019: rkang sgrog lcags kyis rab tu dkris //
NK039(ti)030:1020: phyir phyogs dril gyi pha la bcib //
NK039(ti)030:1021: 'byung po phal cher kun gyis rje mor mthong //
NK039(ti)030:1022: 'byung po phal cher sha la chem chem za //
NK039(ti)030:1023: mi khrag chang gis ra ror myos //
NK039(ti)030:1024: dpag tshad brgyad khri bzhi stong yang //
NK039(ti)030:1025: mtshan mo gcig la khyab par nyul //
NK039(ti)030:1026: song zhig de ni dgra rnams long //
NK039(ti)030:1027: ral pa 'bar ba stong khams mngags /
NK039(ti)030:1028: dgra rnams khrag gis skam gyi rgya mtsho bskyil //
NK039(ti)030:1029: dgra rnams sha ni khyod kyis rgyag mid cig /
NK039(ti)030:1031: dus la babs kyis da zo zhig /
NK039(ti)030:1032: rnal 'byor chen mo a la la //
NK039(ti)030:1033: dbang phyug chen mo a la la //
NK039(ti)030:1034: gshin rje'i lcam mo a la la //
NK039(ti)030:1035: bdud kyi yum gcig a la la //
NK039(ti)030:1036: mdog bzang nag mo a la la //
NK039(ti)030:1037: mtshan bzang re ti a la la /
NK039(ti)030:1039: nad dang rims kyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)030:1041: sku ni mthing nag chen mo la //
NK039(ti)030:1042: bud med nag mos stong khams gang //
NK039(ti)030:1043: ral pa sil bu mun ltar gtib //
NK039(ti)030:1044: spyan nas khrag gi mchi ma 'dzag /
NK039(ti)030:1045: shangs nas nad kyi dud pa 'thul //
NK039(ti)030:1047: g.yas nas zhing gi g.yang gzhi brdeb //
NK039(ti)030:1048: g.yon na nad kyi rkyal pa thogs //
NK039(ti)030:1049: nad dang rims kyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)030:1050: 'dir byon rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)030:1051: sdang ba'i dgra 'di da lta nyid du sod //
NK039(ti)030:1052: rnal 'byor bdag gi bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:1054: ru ru be ti sta pa de sa /
NK039(ti)030:1055: ru ru ro ru be ti sta pa de s+w+aa h+aa /
NK039(ti)030:1057: ru ru ba to rti ba do ma /
NK039(ti)030:1058: ru ru ro tish+tha sa do h'u dzah snying po 'di gal chen lan drug cu brjod gsungs /
NK039(ti)030:1059: gdung ba'i nga ro dbyung nas gtor ma dgra phyogs su 'phang ngo //
NK039(ti)030:1061: gtor ma dpal 'bar gyis mdzes pa la dgug gzhug byas pa btegs /
NK039(ti)030:1063: ma mo'i spyi dril dang 'khor sngags kyi mthar /
NK039(ti)030:1064: sa p+aa ri wa ra sha trum m+aam sa rak+ta
NK039(ti)030:1065: i dam ba limn ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa
NK039(ti)030:1066: hi / lan bdun nam nyer gcig gis phul /
NK039(ti)030:1068: bcom ldan sh+aakya seng ge'i spyan snga ru //
NK039(ti)030:1069: khyod kyis dengs nas 'khor ba ji srid bar //
NK039(ti)030:1070: bstan srungs 'gro skyongs dam bcas phrin las bzhin //
NK039(ti)030:1071: 'dir byon ba ling ri ltar spungs pa dang //
NK039(ti)030:1072: mtsho ltar bskyil ba'i sman rag 'di bzhes shig /
NK039(ti)030:1073: sngar bcol las kyi btang rag gnyen po dang //
NK039(ti)030:1074: da bcol phrin las gnyen po bsgrub phyir bzhes //
NK039(ti)030:1075: dpal ldan ma la phrin las bcol ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:1076: ka chen lha klus byas pa'i gzhal med khang //
NK039(ti)030:1077: kha bad g.yu 'od 'phro ba thod pa'i mkhar //
NK039(ti)030:1078: ga dza mu tig do shal brgyan pa'i mthar //
NK039(ti)030:1079: nga ros 'bod pa'i ma tshogs bye ba yi //
NK039(ti)030:1080: ca cos 'jigs bskyed drag po'i dur khrod gnas //
NK039(ti)030:1081: cha med cir yang 'gyur ba mu le'i mtshor //
NK039(ti)030:1082: ja ril mgo skam lnga yis dbu brgyan cing //
NK039(ti)030:1083: nya rgyas nyi zla'i gtsug dang lte ba'i rgyan //
NK039(ti)030:1084: ta gan bde bar rol mkhas dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)030:1085: tha chad sdang dgra'i snying gzer mche ba gtsigs //
NK039(ti)030:1086: da lta bdag gi mdun 'dir gshegs nas kyang //
NK039(ti)030:1087: na mo sor 'dab g.yo ba'i phyag gis bskur //
NK039(ti)030:1088: pa p+aam sgrib pas kheng ba zhing bcu'i khrag /
NK039(ti)030:1089: pha mtha' yongs bral ting 'dzin gyis brlabs pa'i //
NK039(ti)030:1090: ba glang bya rta khyi sogs sha lnga dang //
NK039(ti)030:1091: ma da na dang bdud rtsi lnga'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)030:1092: tsa tur khrag zhag thal mtshan khyod kyis gsol //
NK039(ti)030:1093: tsha zer nyi ltar 'bar ba'i spyan zung gis //
NK039(ti)030:1094: dza lang bdud sde'i tshogs rnams thal bar rlog /
NK039(ti)030:1095: wa ltar log ltas brgyal ba'i slob bu yang //
NK039(ti)030:1096: zhwa rongs lkug sogs chad pas chom la phob //
NK039(ti)030:1097: za skal khram la btab nas tshon gyis chings //
NK039(ti)030:1098: 'a 'ur me lung 'thab pa'i gur khang nas //
NK039(ti)030:1099: ya ma r+aa dza'i sring gcig bdag cag skyongs /
NK039(ti)030:1100: rwa ba rab dkar gangs ri'i yul ljongs 'dir //
NK039(ti)030:1101: la la tsam min thub bstan bka' drin can //
NK039(ti)030:1102: sha za 'dul mdzad mtsho skyes rdo rje zhes //
NK039(ti)030:1103: sa gsum 'gro ba'i mgon de'i dam mnos ltar //
NK039(ti)030:1104: ha ha snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i legs bshad dang /
NK039(ti)030:1105: a ti'i sgom grwa rgyas pa'i phrin las la //
NK039(ti)030:1106: hi hi'i bzhad sgra 'byin pa khyod gsol na //
NK039(ti)030:1107: a la la ho snying gi bdud rtsir mdzod //
NK039(ti)030:1108: ces thugs dam bskul ba'i rol mo bcas rdo rje shugs rgyas sgrub khang gi steng du bskyal lo //
NK039(ti)030:1110: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa l+ai de wi re ma ti sa p+aa ri wa ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK039(ti)030:1113: ma b+h+yo dza las byung ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)030:1114: ce spyang bong dril 'byung ba bzhi la chibs //
NK039(ti)030:1115: dpal ldan lha mo re ti mched bzhi sogs //
NK039(ti)030:1116: 'khor bcas ma mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)030:1117: bdag ni rang rig ye shessogs /
NK039(ti)030:1118: phur pa las 'byung ba'i brting bshags bya ba'am /
NK039(ti)030:1121: 'khor rnams skem bcas ma mo'i thugs kar thim //
NK039(ti)030:1122: bong bu ma mo la thim /
NK039(ti)030:1123: ma mo yang bdag gi thugs kar thim /
NK039(ti)030:1124: gzhal yas khang dang me rlung yang stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK039(ti)030:1126: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK039(ti)030:1127: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi //
NK039(ti)030:1128: sa la 'gro bas sangs rgyas kyi //
NK039(ti)030:1129: lam de thams cad mthar phyin shog /
NK039(ti)030:1131: rnal 'byor ma dpal snying rje'i bdud rtsi las //
NK039(ti)030:1132: yum gyur rdo rje'i rigs te bu la brtse //
NK039(ti)030:1133: gtum chen rngams ma rgyud kyi bstan pa bsrungs //
NK039(ti)030:1134: gsang ba dbyings phyug mkha' 'gro'i bkra shis shog /
NK039(ti)030:1135: de ltar gong ma'i gsungs bzang legs bshad kyi //
NK039(ti)030:1136: lang tshos rnam 'khyud snying gi mdza' na mo //
NK039(ti)030:1137: don mthun skal bzang tshogs la skyes su byin //
NK039(ti)030:1138: 'dod don bde mgul rol phyir brten par rigs //
NK039(ti)030:1139: de las thob pa'i rnam dkar dge ba ni //
NK039(ti)030:1140: ti se brtsegs ma'i gangs ri las 'ongs lta //
NK039(ti)030:1141: dge tshogs chu rlung ma lus gcig bsdus nas //
NK039(ti)030:1142: rnam mkhyen rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i phyir bsngo'o //
NK039(ti)030:1143: de ltar rgyud dang man ngag kun gyi bcud 'gal med du bsdebs pa 'di'ang /
NK039(ti)030:1144: bla ma kahthoga pa'i zhabs sen snying la rtag tu
NK039(ti)030:1145: gnas pas gsang chen rgyud sde rin po che la
NK039(ti)030:1146: blo gros kyi snang ba cung zad rgyas pa sh+aakya'i
NK039(ti)030:1147: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa chos kyi rgya mtshos
NK039(ti)030:1148: / shar kahthoga gi yang dben bkra shis bde ldan gling du sbyar ba dge legs 'phel //
